longBusinessSummary: MTI Investment AB (publ) is principal firm specializing in high-growth small and medium-sized firms. The firm seeks to invests in Eastern Africa. The firm will not engage in the production of tobacco or alcohol, or gambling and casino businesses. The firm typical invests in Eastern Africa. It invests initial investment minimum $1 million turnover, and with long-term growth prospects of at least 15% growth per year (target growth rate of +30%). The firm invests in SMEs that can become a national or regional champion with sales at least $10 million. MTI Investment AB (publ) was founded in 2014 and based in Stockholm, Sweden.
